Victorino Chua is accused of murdering three patients at Stepping Hill Hospital in Stockport . 
  He denies murdering Tracey Arden, 44, Arnold Lancaster, 71 and Derek Weaver, 83 . 
  Chua also denies deliberately poisoning 18 others at the hospital in 2011 and 2012 . 
  He has given evidence for the first time and denied he tampered with saline bags and ampoules . 
  The 49-year-old said he did not contaminate medicine with insulin . 
  He is also accused of deliberately altering prescription charts at hospital . 
  He said he was 'an evil person' and made a 'bitter nurse confession' Chua has pleaded not guilty to 36 charges at Stockport Crown Court . 
 